{"en":[{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:41.228","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:41.478","Content":"Trying to do."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:44.828","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:45.078","Content":"And I want to thank the"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:46.561","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:46.811","Content":"committee members for showing up"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:48.828","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:49.078","Content":"on the Saturday morning. Uh, we"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:49.495","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:49.745","Content":"appreciate it. There is"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:50.061","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:50.311","Content":"breakfast."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:54.561","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:54.811","Content":"And the breakfast is from Sierra"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:55.261","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:55.511","Content":"Sierra Club."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:56.761","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:57.011","Content":"So thank you very much, Sierra"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:58.795","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:59.045","Content":"Club for our breakfast burritos"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:06:59.461","End":"2025-02-15T09:06:59.711","Content":"this morning. So Senator Pope,"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:00.828","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:01.078","Content":"it's yours."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:05.328","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:05.578","Content":"Thank you and a three piece suit"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:05.995","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:06.245","Content":"today. OK."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:09.295","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:09.545","Content":"Yeah, we're gonna present today"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:10.861","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:11.111","Content":"Senate Bill 178."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:14.528","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:14.778","Content":"And really there are two parts"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:15.228","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:15.478","Content":"to this bill. The first part"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:17.028","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:17.278","Content":"involves the imposition of a fee"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:18.761","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:19.011","Content":"of 5 cents per barrel of"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:20.795","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:21.045","Content":"produced water on owners of oil"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:21.495","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:21.745","Content":"and gas wells in New Mexico."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:24.761","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:25.011","Content":"The fee imposed is referred to"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:25.461","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:25.711","Content":"as the produced water ee."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:27.061","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:27.311","Content":"reduced water fee will be"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:28.761","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:29.011","Content":"collected and administered by"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:29.428","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:29.678","Content":"the Taxation and Revenue"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:31.061","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:31.311","Content":"Department and then sent to the"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:32.561","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:32.811","Content":"Energy, Minerals and Natural"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:33.228","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:33.478","Content":"Resources Department for"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:34.861","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:35.111","Content":"plugging and remediating"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:35.428","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:35.678","Content":"abandoned wells."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:37.228","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:37.478","Content":"The Environment Department"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:38.961","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:39.211","Content":"estimates that this fee will"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:39.628","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:39.878","Content":"amount to $68 million per year."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:43.095","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:43.345","Content":"And the FIR estimates around 80."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:45.028","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:45.278","Content":"To $95 million."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:48.961","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:49.211","Content":"In 2021, the state land Office"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:51.028","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:51.278","Content":"projected an $8.1 billion dollar"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:52.761","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:53.011","Content":"gap between bonds and actual"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:55.028","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:55.278","Content":"remediation costs, a number that"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:56.828","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:57.078","Content":"continues to increase as"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:58.528","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:58.778","Content":"financial assurances do not meet"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:07:59.395","End":"2025-02-15T09:07:59.645","Content":"the actual costs of plugging and"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:00.061","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:00.311","Content":"remediation."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:04.828","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:05.078","Content":"There are more than 2,391"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:06.595","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:06.845","Content":"abandoned wells on state or"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:07.228","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:07.478","Content":"private land, but there are"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:08.795","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:09.045","Content":"thousands more wells that are"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:09.395","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:09.645","Content":"known as orphans and waiting."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:12.861","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:13.111","Content":"Enert estimates that the average"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:14.761","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:15.011","Content":"cost of plug and remediate a"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:17.228","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:17.478","Content":"single well is $300,000 but some"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:17.895","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:18.145","Content":"cost $1 million."},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:20.995","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:21.245","Content":"The risks of unplugging wells"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:22.561","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:22.811","Content":"are enormous. The environmental"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:23.328","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:23.578","Content":"and health issues are mainly the"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:24.828","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:25.078","Content":"release of large amounts of"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:26.828","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:27.078","Content":"methane, a potent greenhouse gas"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:28.795","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:29.045","Content":"and groundwater contamination,"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:30.561","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:30.811","Content":"which can introduce carcinogenic"},{"Begin":"2025-02-15T09:08:31.261","End":"2025-02-15T09:08:31.511","Content":"chemicals in the drinking water."}]}